NATO intends to make Putin realize that the only way to avoid his forces being wiped out altogether is to withdraw them and declare that he has done all he needed to do - a Pyrrhic victory at best. Ryan
1 hour ago (edited)
The Tsunami in Japan released the energy equivalent to 500 megatons of wave energy and created an approximate 100 foot Tidal wave. The total energy from the quake was 9.3 million megatons. Given that only 50 percent of a nuclear blasts energy is released as blast, the rest is heat and radiation in theory you would need a 1,000 megaton bomb to get a 100' wave. Since the height of the wave is not linear with the equivalent explosion and rather exponential, if you detonated the entire worlds arsenals at a single point in the ocean it would not create a tidal wave 500m in height, not even close.
